data.description: Great turn key condo!  Well kept with newer carpet, paint, and all new plumbing.  Ready to move in, all appliances included.  Private yard, mature landscape, close to all amenities.  It doesnt get any easier than this!  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from Weber county .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
